<normalizedToken id="6C31EE50AA5ECDAB5267B1080A6F17C6" originalValue="Schmalblättrige" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Schmalblaettrige</normalizedToken>
Lupine
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="61A6F08AD76CEB1A6983CD61B05E9DF9" pageId="null" pageNumber="487" type="description">
<paragraph id="C77ED042E66067B79AAA86211A79C2CB" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
1 
<normalizedToken id="A45DDE6F1C7709E88B44047B265861D6" originalValue="jährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">jaehrig</normalizedToken>
; 20-120 cm hoch. 
<emphasis id="5D1B599D167F66E132E522359D7E5646" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<normalizedToken id="5F75FE5AA05A4E559F79661716A98B5B" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
5-9
</emphasis>
, schmal lanzettlich, 1-5 cm lang und 
<emphasis id="2058BAA802554804970E98F96E53ADFC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">0,2-0,5 cm breit</emphasis>
, meist stumpf, unterseits anliegend behaart (Haare 0,5-1 mm lang), oberseits fast kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="F5B99F2CA755638DF3DED626AEFA14D0" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
10-20 cm lang, auf 1-3 cm langem Stiel. 
<normalizedToken id="A7211AEDA4137732DE52D021FB0BD4CF" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Blueten</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="0B4888D1B4E00E8CF80F6108AB912048" originalValue="wechselständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">wechselstaendig</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="AC87182BBCABB65D225A64245FEEFEB2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Krone 1-1,3 cm lang, hellblau</emphasis>
(selten 
<normalizedToken id="38ED240AAD4106E7C950444A2C5523E0" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">weiss</normalizedToken>
, purpurn oder mehrfarbig). Frucht 4-7 cm lang und 1-1,2 cm breit, anliegend behaart. Samen 
<normalizedToken id="76321F26060CCA8E84CCA1396DC22D64" originalValue="eiförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">eifoermig</normalizedToken>
, 6-10 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="8CF1548AC3B3E2A46EFDEC0D0BA0D536" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="C1CADF61B075189BC7F3E16C186AB8EF" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="1E5F6685821FDE105CB55613D3E82D2C" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1F545AB617DE1A5BAFA4E0DA0ADC34EA" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis id="37B8B0997772889A0F348B67B13E1CEC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="DD8551DADE6BD5689F51D9105D636B7F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">40</emphasis>
(Winge aus Kawakami 1930; Malheiros 1942, Atabekova 1959, Gilot 1965). 
<emphasis id="DE22CB22597A9FB3D8E421B5FB9CCD30" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="ED080EB8D900BC612A5A7490AB3D673A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">48</emphasis>
(Kawakami 1930). Alles Material unbekannter Herkunft.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BA067DEEA765A0B43324F53D370C80D1" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis id="5FB5CDC17AE1A3AA8B85EB7C0489C48F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Kalkarme, sandige 
<normalizedToken id="A621C55419C4DABF293A8C6FA69E7395" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="68BD4712AD63B2BF38B4DA5C798BC437" originalValue="wärmeren" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">waermeren</normalizedToken>
Lagen. Felder, unbebaute 
<normalizedToken id="6A108FB56D3309B3B207D627CF3A4E44" originalValue="Plätze" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Plaetze</normalizedToken>
, Geleiseanlagen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="02D0188140C07AF807C7A4143C40D73C" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis id="6546145A5489C3150D61338E873A0901" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="487">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze.</emphasis>
- Im Gebiet gelegentlich angepflanzt und selten verwildert.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
